<F P=100> BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Two Civilians Wounded in Muslim Attack on Teslic </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Two Civilians Wounded in Muslim Attack on Teslic </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1406104394 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1003 GMT 14 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1406104394 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Doboj, 14 Jun (TANJUG) -- Muslim forces have been 
active on all battlefields in the Doboj area, the information 
service of the republic of Srpska army's 1st Krajina Corps said 
today. Muslims fired several artillery shells on Teslic from 
the direction of Tesanj. Two civilians were injured in the 
attack and material damage was caused. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

