  [Text] The aggressor did not stop attacks in the theater 
of operations of the 7 South Operations Group either. 
  [Unidentified reporter] In the last 24 hours, the chetniks 
have also been shelling civilian targets in Tesanj, Jelah, 
Tesanjica, and other settlements on this free territory. The 
residents of Tesanj are still in shelters as the aggressor is 
pounding the city center. One eight-year-old boy was killed 
during the shelling last night. Several persons sustained 
