<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Mistrust for Coming Census"] </F>
  [Text] The Association of Serbs and Montenegrins in 
Macedonia [The Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia -- FYROM] 
cannot accept the results and the census itself as objective, 
representatives of the association said at yesterday's press 
conference. The association president Nebojsa Tomovic said the 
census will be just another step towards federalization of 
Macedonia and meeting the demands of Albanians at the cost of 
the Serbian population in Macedonia, whose real number is 
minimized. The association announced an inner census only for 
the Serbian minority, in order to come up with exact figures of 
Serbs living in Macedonia. 

